/blob/v2.8.0/mindspore/python/mindspore/ops/operations/nn_ops.py#L417\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#mindspore.ops.Mish\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\"></a></dt>\n<dd><p>Computes MISH(A Self Regularized Non-Monotonic Neural Activation Function) of input tensors element-wise.</p>\n<p>Refer to <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"mindspore.ops.mish.html#mindspore.ops.mish\" title=\"mindspore.ops.mish\"><code class=\"xref py py-func docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">mindspore.ops.mish()</span></code></a> for more details.</p>\n<dl class=\"simple\">\n<dt>Inputs:</dt><dd><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>x</strong> (Tensor) - The input Tensor.\nSupported dtypes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>GPU/CPU: float16, float32, float64.</p></li>\n<li><p>Ascend: float16, float32.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n<dt>Outputs:</dt><dd><p>Tensor, with the same type and shape as the <cite>x</cite>.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt>Supported Platforms:</dt><dd><p><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">Ascend</span></code> <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">GPU</span></code> <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">CPU</span></code></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"doctest highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">mindspore</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">numpy</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">as</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">np</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">mindspore</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Tensor</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">ops</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Tensor</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">np</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">array</span><span class=\"p\">([[</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">1.0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">4.0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">8.0</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mf\">2.0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">5.0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mf\">9.0</span><span class=\"p\">]]),</span> <span class=\"n\">mindspore</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">float32</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">mish</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">ops</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Mish</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">output</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mish</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">output</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"go\">(2, 3)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Tensor</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mf\">2.1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">mindspore</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">float32</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">output</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mish</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">output</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"go\">2.050599</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</dd></dl>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<footer><div aria-label=\"Footer\" class=\"rst-footer-buttons\" role=\"navigation\">\n<a accesskey=\"p\" class=\"btn btn-neutral float-left\" href=\"mindspore.ops.LogSoftmax.html\" rel=\"prev\" title=\"mindspore.ops.LogSoftmax\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-left\"></span> Previous</a>\n<a accesskey=\"n\" class=\"btn btn-neutral float-right\" href=\"mindspore.ops.PReLU.html\" rel=\"next\" title=\"mindspore.ops.PReLU\">Next <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></span></a>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<div role=\"contentinfo\">\n<p>© Copyright MindSpore.</p>\n</div>\n\n  Built with <a href=\"https://www.sphinx-doc.org/\">Sphinx</a> using a\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/readthedocs/sphinx_rtd_theme\">theme</a>\n    provided by <a href=\"https://readthedocs.org\">Read the Docs</a>.\n   \n\n</footer>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<script>\n      jQuery(function () {\n          SphinxRtdTheme.Navigation.enable(true);\n      });\n  </script>\n</body>"
